chunk_content: DREAMS program completion requires I O that an individual AGYW has completed both the primary package for her age group, as well as all N secondary interventions that are appropriate based on her needs. An AGYW must have completed at least 1 service in the past 6 months at Q2 or the past 12 months at Q4 to be counted in any of the following disaggregates: “completed the full primary package and no additional services,” “completed the primary package and at least 1 additional service,” or “completed at least 1 service but not the full primary package.” At Q2 and Q4 reporting, AGYW should be reported under the disaggregate that reflects the snapshot of her current layering status since beginning the DREAMS program.
